de.rincewind.api.gui.elements.abstracts

Interface ElementSlot

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Element, EventBased
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ElementInput, ElementOutput, ElementScanner
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CraftElementInput, CraftElementOutput, CraftElementScanner, CraftElementSlot, Elements.ElementInputExtendable, Elements.ElementOutputExtendable, Elements.ElementScannerExtendable, Elements.ElementSlotExtendable

    public interface ElementSlot
extends Element
    The element is an empty slot to let the user drop items in or pick something out of it. If this element is disabled, in the slot will be set a barrier and the ClickBlocker will be locked.
    Since:
    2.3.3
    Author:
    Rincewind34
